Package: tidyweb
Type: Package
Title: Easily Install and Load Modern Web-Scraping Packages
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2017-08-30
Author: Bob Rudis (bob@rud.is)
Maintainer: Bob Rudis <bob@rud.is>
Description: Scraping the modern web requires having many tools in one's toolbox
    and the 'tidyverse' only enables easy installation and loading of a few, core
    ones. `tidyweb` bundles a more complete list of scraping tools to make it easier
    to both install and use them.
URL: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/tidyweb
BugReports: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/tidyweb/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    curl,
    jsonlite,
    httr,
    xml2,
    rvest,
    purrr,
    dplyr,
    stringi,
    gdns,
    urltools,
    iptools,
    seleniumPipes,
    HARtools,
    xslt,
    V8,
    webreadr,
    openssl,
    splashr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
